-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() load = input.getNumber(1) loadb= (load/100)*43 end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) screen.drawClear() screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawTextBox(0, 0, w, h, "Loading", 0, 0) screen.drawRect(0+10, 38, w-20, 5) screen.drawRectF(0+11, 39, loadb, 5)
end

-- Tick function that will be executed every logic tick function onTick() a = input.getNumber(1)
temp1 = input.getNumber(2)
t1 = input.getNumber(3) bar= (t1/1)*(-12)
t2 = input.getNumber(4) bar1= (t2/1)*(-12)
b = input.getNumber(5)
temp2 = input.getNumber(6)
end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 0, 0) -- Set draw color to green screen.drawCircleF(w / 2, h / 2, 30) screen.drawClear()
screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawRect(0, 0, 32, 63) screen.drawRect(32, 0, 31, 63)
screen.drawCircle(20, 50, 8) screen.drawCircle(49, 50, 8) screen.drawCircle(20, 25, 8) screen.drawCircle(49, 25, 8)
screen.drawRect(7, 44, 3, 12) screen.drawRectF(7, 57, 3, bar)
screen.drawRect(36, 44, 3, 12) screen.drawRectF(36, 57, 3, bar1)
screen.setColor(100, 0, 0) screen.drawTextBox(12, 51, w-20, 2, string.format("%.0f", a), 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(-17, 51, w-20, 2, string.format("%.0f", b), 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(12, 26, w-20, 2, string.format("%.0f", temp2), 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(-17, 26, w-20, 2, string.format("%.0f", temp1), 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(12, 40, w-20, 2, "RPS", 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(-17, 40, w-20, 2, "RPS", 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(17, 15, w-20, 2, "Temp", 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(-13, 15, w-20, 2, "Temp", 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(16, 5, w-20, 2, "Eng 2", 1, 1) screen.drawTextBox(-17, 5, w-20, 2, "Eng 1", 1, 1)
end

function onTick() gN,gB=input.getNumber,input.getBool thr=gN(1) bl1,bl2=gB(1),gB(2) end
function onDraw() dT,dTB,sC,flr,sin,pi=screen.drawText,screen.drawTextBox,screen.setColor,math.floor,math.sin,math.pi w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() thr=flr(thr*100+.5)/100 sC(0,0,0) screen.drawClear() bFH=flr(h*.6-1) bRH=flr(h*.4-1) mid=flr(h*.6) sC(60,60,60) screen.drawRect(0,0,10,h-1) screen.drawRect(12,0,19,8) dT(12,mid-2,math.abs(flr(thr*100)).."%") if thr>0 then blink(0,255,0,bl1) screen.drawRectF(13,1,18,7) blink(0,255,0,bl1,true) dTB(13,1,19,8,"FWD",0,0) sC(0,255,0) elseif thr<0 then blink(255,0,0,bl2) screen.drawRectF(13,1,18,7) blink(255,0,0,bl2,true) dTB(13,1,19,8,"REV",0,0) sC(255,0,0) else sC(200,40,0) screen.drawRectF(13,1,18,7) sC(0,0,0) dTB(13,1,19,8,"---",0,0) sC(200,40,0) end screen.drawLine(1,mid,10,mid) if thr>0 then bH=bFH*sin(thr*pi/2) dStep=200/bFH for i=1,bH do sC(0,180,0,i*dStep+55) screen.drawLine(1,mid-i,10,mid-i) end elseif thr<0 then bH=bRH*sin(thr*pi/2*-1) dStep=200/bRH for i=1,bH do sC(200,0,0,i*dStep+55) screen.drawLine(1,mid+i,10,mid+i) end end end
function blink(r,g,b,blkr,inv) if (blkr and not inv) or (not blkr and inv) then sC(r,g,b) else sC(0,0,0) end end

object.script:
cyan={42,252,90,(42)/10,(102)/10,(90)/10} red={150,25,24,10,5,4} pink={253,43,218,10,4,9} white={150,150,150,10,10,10} blue={42,252,218,4,4,11} yellow={225,253,44,23,26,0} -- this is the fuel & battery display t=0 lvl=0 function onTick() lvlp=lvl theme=input.getNumber(1) spd =input.getNumber(2) rps =input.getNumber(3) lvl =input.getNumber(4) cap =input.getNumber(5) bat =input.getNumber(6) mxspd=input.getNumber(7) mxrps=input.getNumber(8) x =input.getNumber(9) show =input.getNumber(10)
on =input.getBool(1) blink=input.getBool(2) use =input.getBool(3) fix =input.getBool(8) and 1 or 0 if on then t=math.min(t+1,100) else t=math.max(t-2,0) end c=t/100 if use then hi = 24 else hi = 18 end if theme==0 then dig=cyan elseif theme==1 then dig=red elseif theme==2 then dig=pink elseif theme==3 then dig=white elseif theme==4 then dig=blue else dig=yellow end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawClear()
screen.setColor(dig[4],dig[5],dig[6]) screen.drawRectF(1,1+x+fix,w-2,hi)
screen.setColor(dig[1],dig[2],dig[3],c*255) if lvl/cap>show then fuel="fuel" else fuel=math.floor(lvl).."L" end
screen.drawText(2,4+x,fuel) fuelblip=math.floor(lvl/cap*4+0.5) for i=0,fuelblip,1 do if i<fuelblip then screen.drawRect(2+i*5,2+x,3,0) elseif i==fuelblip and blink then screen.drawRect(2+i*5,2+x,3,0) end end
screen.drawText(2,13+x,"batt.") batteryblip=math.floor(bat*4+0.5) for i=0,batteryblip,1 do if i<batteryblip then screen.drawRect(2+i*5,11+x,3,0) elseif i==batteryblip and blink then screen.drawRect(2+i*5,11+x,3,0) end end if use then lps = math.min(math.floor((lvlp-lvl)*60*10),999) if string.len(lps)<2 then unit="dl/s"elseif string.len(lps)<3 then unit="dls" else unit="dl" end screen.drawText(2,19+x,lps..unit) end screen.drawLine(0,h-1,w,h-1) end

cyan={42,252,90,(42)/10,(102)/10,(90)/10} red={150,25,24,10,5,4} pink={253,43,218,10,4,9} white={150,150,150,10,10,10} blue={42,252,218,4,4,11} yellow={225,253,44,23,26,0} t=0 pos=0 function lne(x) y=1-math.abs(x*2%(2*1)-1) return y end -- this is the script for speed
function onTick() theme=input.getNumber(1) spd =input.getNumber(2) rps =input.getNumber(3) lvl =input.getNumber(4) cap =input.getNumber(5) bat =input.getNumber(6) mxspd=input.getNumber(7) mxrps=input.getNumber(8) x =input.getNumber(9) unit =input.getNumber(12)
on =input.getBool(1) blink=input.getBool(2)
lines=input.getBool(7) fix =input.getBool(8) and 1 or 0 if on then t=math.min(t+1,100) else t=math.max(t-2,0) end c=t/100 if unit<1.5 then km="ms^" un=1 elseif unit>3 then km="km^" un=3.6 else km="mi^" un=2.23694 end if unit==1.94384 then km="knt" un=1.94384 end --wedge knots in spdper=math.min(1,spd/(mxspd/un)) pos=(pos+spdper/10)%1 if theme==0 then dig=cyan elseif theme==1 then dig=red elseif theme==2 then dig=pink elseif theme==3 then dig=white elseif theme==4 then dig=blue elseif theme==5 then dig=yellow end end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawClear()
screen.setColor(dig[4],dig[5],dig[6]) --bg
screen.drawRectF(1,1+x+fix,5*3+1,7) screen.drawText(18,2+x,km)
screen.setColor(dig[1]/4,dig[2]/4,dig[3]/4,c*255) --fg sec.
screen.drawLine(0,h-1,w,h-1) screen.drawLine(0,h-1,w/2,h/2-1) screen.drawLine(w-1,h-1,w/2-1,h/2-1)
screen.setColor(dig[1],dig[2],dig[3],c*255) --fg
screen.drawText(2,2+x,string.format( "%03d" , math.floor(spd * un+0.5)))
screen.drawLine(spdper*w/2-0.5, h-1-h/2*spdper, w-math.ceil(spdper*w/2-0.5), h-1-h/2*spdper) if lines and spd>10 then ya=math.max(pos*h,h/2) yb=lne(pos)*h/2 screen.drawRectF(w/2-1,ya,2,yb) screen.drawLine(w-ya-1,ya,w-ya-yb-1,ya+yb) screen.drawLine(ya,ya,ya+yb,ya+yb) end end

object.script:
gBl=input.getBool gNm=input.getNumber
clr=screen.setColor txt=screen.drawText lne=screen.drawLine rctF=screen.drawRectF tri=screen.drawTriangle triF=screen.drawTriangleF
ba=0
function onTick() p = gNm(1) -- pitch angle ba1 = gNm(2) -- bank angle inv = gNm(3) -- inverted angle
blnk = gBl(1) fdEnable = gBl(5) dualCue = gBl(6) fdP = gNm(5) fdR = gNm(6)-0.1
if inv < 0 then ba = 180-ba1 else ba = ba1 end
end
function onDraw() w = 96 h = 32 a1 = h/2+1 -- center height b1 = w/2 -- center width
--p1 = p+a r = 1.5*w o = math.rad(ba) -- bank angle radians co = math.rad(fdR) soh = math.sin(o) cah = math.cos(o) fdsoh = math.sin(o-co) fdcah = math.cos(o-co) a = a1+(p*cah) -- center of rotation for horizon x value b = b1+(p*soh) -- center of rotation for horizon y value y1 = r*soh x1 = r*cah r2 = 90+(2*w) x2 = r2*soh y2 = r2*cah
clr(5, 20, 60) triF(-x1+b, y1+a, x1+b, -y1+a, -x2+b, -y2+a) -- sky clr(25, 10, 0) triF(-x1+b, y1+a, x1+b, -y1+a, x2+b, y2+a) -- ground
clr(220,220,220) --draw horizon lne(-x1+b, y1+a-cah, x1+b, -y1+a-cah) --create 10 degree lines for i = 80, -80, -10 do if i ~= 0 then cx = i*soh cy = i*cah lne((-4*cah)+cx+b, (4*soh)+cy+a, (4*cah)+cx+b, (-4*soh)+cy+a) end end
--create X at 90 degrees up/down clr(255, 0, 0) for i=1,-1,-2 do cxu1, cyu1, cxu2, cyu2 = i*86*soh, i*86*cah, i*94*soh, i*94*cah lne((-7*cah)+cxu1+b, (7*soh)+cyu1+a, (7*cah)+cxu2+b, (-7*soh)+cyu2+a) lne((-7*cah)+cxu2+b, (7*soh)+cyu2+a, (7*cah)+cxu1+b, (-7*soh)+cyu1+a) end
--flight director if fdEnable then clr(255,0,255) if not dualCue then --single cue flight director (v-bars) cx = fdP*soh cy = fdP*cah
--right side triangle Ax1, Ay1 = (-1*fdcah)+cx+b, cy+a-2 Bx1, By1 = (5*fdcah)+cx+b, (-5*fdsoh)+cy+a-2 Cx1, Cy1 = Bx1+4*fdsoh, By1+4*fdcah Dx1, Dy1 = Cx1+7*fdcah, Cy1-7*fdsoh triF(Ax1, Ay1, Bx1, By1, Cx1, Cy1) triF(Bx1, By1, Cx1, Cy1, Dx1, Dy1)
--left side triangle Ax2, Ay2 = cx+b, cy+a-2 Bx2, By2 = (-6*fdcah)+cx+b, (6*fdsoh)+cy+a-2 Cx2, Cy2 = Bx2+4*fdsoh, By2+4*fdcah Dx2, Dy2 = Cx2-7*fdcah, Cy2+7*fdsoh triF(Ax2, Ay2, Bx2, By2, Cx2, Cy2) triF(Bx2, By2, Cx2, Cy2, Dx2, Dy2)
--warning when off screen if Dy1 < 6 and Dy2 < 6 then if blnk then lne(47,8,43,12) lne(48,8,52,12) end elseif Dy1 > 34 and Dy2 > 34 then if blnk then lne(47,30,43,26) lne(48,30,52,26) end end elseif dualCue then --dual cue flight director --pitch bar pB = -fdP-p
if 15-pB < 4 then pBy = 4 elseif 15-pB > 28 then pBy = 28 else pBy = 15-pB end rctF(33, pBy, 30, 2)
--roll bar rB = ba - fdR
if 47-rB < 32 then rBx = 32 elseif 47-rB > 62 then rBx = 62 else rBx = 47-rB end rctF(rBx, 3, 2, 26) end
end
--center piece of artificial horizon clr(120, 120, 0) if not dualCue then triF(b1, a1-2, b1-5, a1+3, b1+5, a1+3) lne(b1-14, a1-2, b1-7, a1-2) lne(b1+7, a1-2, b1+14, a1-2) elseif dualCue then lne(b1-14, a1-2, b1-7, a1-2) lne(b1+7, a1-2, b1+14, a1-2) lne(b1-7, a1-2, b1-7, a1+1) lne(b1+6, a1-2, b1+6, a1+1) rctF(b1-1, a1-2, 2, 2) end end

gNm=input.getNumber gBl=input.getBool sBl=output.setBool
clr=screen.setColor f=255 txt=screen.drawText rct=screen.drawRect rctF=screen.drawRectF lne=screen.drawLine tri=screen.drawTriangleF
function onTick() ap=gBl(1) labels=gBl(2) hdgToggle=gBl(3)
heading=gNm(1) bug=gNm(2)
gradientToggle=gBl(4) marginType=gNm(3) --1=none 2=translucent 3=opaque end
function round(val,places,label) return string.format("%." .. (places or 0) .. "f", val) .. label end
function onDraw()
if hdgToggle then
--draw black band clr(0,0,0,200) rctF(29,0,38,2)
--draw heading tape for i=0,38,1 do if heading-(i-19) < 0 then headingOffset=360+heading-(i-17) elseif heading-(i-19) > 360 then headingOffset=heading-(i-19)-360 else headingOffset=heading-(i-19) end if headingOffset%10 == 0 then clr(220, 220, 220) rctF(66-i,0,2,1) end
--determine heading bug position t=(bug-heading+540)%360-180
if t < -18 then headingBugPos=29 elseif t > 18 then headingBugPos=65 else if headingOffset == bug or ((headingOffset == 0 or headingOffset == 360) and (bug == 0 or bug == 360)) then headingBugPos = 66-i end end end
--draw pointer clr(f,f,0) rctF(47,0,2,1)
--determine what to be displayed if labels then if heading == 360 or heading == 0 then headingPrint = "N" elseif heading == 45 then headingPrint = "NE" elseif heading == 90 then headingPrint = "E" elseif heading == 135 then headingPrint = "SE" elseif heading == 180 then headingPrint = "S" elseif heading == 225 then headingPrint = "SW" elseif heading == 270 then headingPrint = "W" elseif heading == 315 then headingPrint = "NW" else headingPrint = round(heading,0,"") end else headingPrint = round(heading,0,"") end
--draw black box clr(0,0,0,200) if string.len(headingPrint) == 2 then boxOffset=-3 elseif string.len(headingPrint) == 3 then boxOffset=-5 else boxOffset=0 end printOffset=(string.len(headingPrint)-1)*-2.5 --keep text centered rctF(45+boxOffset,2,6-2*printOffset,6)
--draw heading clr(220, 220, 220) txt(46+printOffset,2,headingPrint)
--draw heading bug if ap then clr(21,200,238) lne(headingBugPos-1,0,headingBugPos+3,0) lne(headingBugPos,1,headingBugPos+2,1) end
end
--draw the gradient and side margins depending on user selected options if gradientToggle and marginType == 1 then for i=1,48,1 do clr(0,0,0,i*(75/48)) lne(47+i,0,47+i,32) lne(48-i,0,48-i,32) end for i=1,16,1 do clr(0,0,0,i*(75/16)) lne(0,16-i,96,16-i) lne(0,15+i,96,15+i) end elseif gradientToggle and (marginType == 2 or marginType == 3) then for i=1,19,1 do clr(0,0,0,i*(50/19)) lne(47+i,0,47+i,32) lne(48-i,0,48-i,32) end for i=1,16,1 do clr(0,0,0,i*(50/16)) lne(29,16-i,67,16-i) lne(29,15+i,67,15+i) end end if marginType == 2 then clr(0,0,0,125) rctF(0,0,29,32) rctF(67,0,29,32) elseif marginType == 3 then clr(0,0,0) rctF(0,0,29,32) rctF(67,0,29,32) end end

gNm=input.getNumber gBl=input.getBool sBl=output.setBool
clr=screen.setColor f=255 txt=screen.drawText rct=screen.drawRect rctF=screen.drawRectF lne=screen.drawLine tri=screen.drawTriangleF
feet=true
speedTapeScale=13 --pixels per 1000 units
function onTick() --multiply meters my unitMulti to convert unit unitMulti=gNm(8)
apEnabled=gBl(2) altSelect=gNm(7)*unitMulti-5
txtBoxEnable=gBl(3) alt=gNm(5)*unitMulti vs=gNm(6)*3.28084*60 maxVs=gNm(9) end
function round(val,places,label) return string.format("%." .. (places or 0) .. "f", val) .. label end
function onDraw() --altitude tape clr(220, 220, 220) lne(67,0,67,32) for i=0,32,1 do altOffset=alt-((i-15)*(1000/speedTapeScale)) altThousands=tonumber(round(altOffset,0,"")) altCheck=tonumber(round(altThousands % 1000,0,"")) if alt-((32-15)*(1000/speedTapeScale)) > altSelect then altBugPos=32 elseif alt-((0-15)*(1000/speedTapeScale)) < altSelect then altBugPos=0 elseif (altOffset-altSelect) < (1000/speedTapeScale) and (altOffset-altSelect) > -(1000/speedTapeScale) then altBugPos=i end if altOffset < 0 then clr(f,0,0) lne(68,i,71,i) elseif altCheck < 1000/speedTapeScale then lne(68,i,71,i) lne(68,i-(speedTapeScale/2),71,i-(speedTapeScale/2)) lne(68,i+(speedTapeScale/2),71,i+(speedTapeScale/2)) txt(72,i-2,round(altOffset/1000,0,"")) end end
--vertical Speed Tape clr(f,0,f) lne(66,16,66,15-((vs/maxVs)*16))
--altitude lable textbox if txtBoxEnable then if alt <= 9999.5 then clr(0,0,0) rctF(71,12,(string.len(round(alt,0,""))*5)+1,7) clr(80,80,80) rct(70,11,(string.len(round(alt,0,""))*5)+2,8) else clr(0,0,0) rctF(71,12,23,7) clr(80,80,80) rct(70,11,24,8) end else clr(0,0,0,250) rctF(68,12,28,7) end
--altitude lable if alt < -1 then clr(f,0,0) else clr(220,220,220) end --if alt >9999 then display decimal thousands if alt <= 9999.5 then txt(72,13,round(alt,0,"")) else txt(72,13,round(math.floor(alt/1000),0,"")) txt(81,13,".") txt(84,13,string.format(tostring(math.floor(((alt/1000)%1)*10))) .. "k") end clr(150,150,0) tri(66,13,66,19,70,16) lne(66,13,66,18)
--altitude bug if apEnabled then clr(21,200,238) tri(67,altBugPos-3,67,altBugPos+3,70,altBugPos) end end

gNm=input.getNumber gBl=input.getBool sBl=output.setBool
clr=screen.setColor f=255 txt=screen.drawText rct=screen.drawRect rctF=screen.drawRectF lne=screen.drawLine tri=screen.drawTriangleF
knots=true
speedTapeScale=1 --pixels per unit
accelDamp=false accel=0 accelPrint=0 accelSens=40 --lower is more sensitive maxAccel=15 --meters per second squared
function onTick() apEnabled=gBl(2) speedSelect=gNm(10)
blnk=gBl(1) txtBoxEnable=gBl(3) speedBandColors=gBl(4) speed=gNm(5) Vs=gNm(7) Va=gNm(8) Vne=gNm(9)
--dampen acceleration to prevent erraticity if not accelDamp then accelLast=accel end accel=gNm(6)*60 if accel>accelLast+(maxAccel/(accelSens)) and accelPrint < maxAccel then accelDamp=true accelPrint=accelLast+(maxAccel/(accelSens)) accelLast=accelPrint elseif accel<accelLast-(maxAccel/(accelSens)) and accelPrint > -maxAccel then accelDamp=true accelPrint=accelLast-(maxAccel/(accelSens)) accelLast=accelPrint elseif accel<accelLast-(maxAccel/(accelSens)) or accel>accelLast+(maxAccel/(accelSens)) then accelDamp=true accelPrint=accelLast else accelDamp=false accelPrint=accel end end
function round(val,places,label) return string.format("%." .. (places or 0) .. "f", val) .. label end
function onDraw() --airspeed tape clr(220, 220, 220) lne(28,0,28,32) for i=-2,34,1 do speedOffset=tonumber(round(speed,0,""))-((i-15)/speedTapeScale) speedCheck=tonumber(round(speedOffset % 10,0,"")) if speedOffset < 0 then clr(f,0,0) lne(27,i,24,i) elseif speedCheck < 1 then clr(220, 220, 220) lne(27,i,24,i) txt(25-(string.len(round(speedOffset,0,""))*5),i-2,round(speedOffset,0,"")) elseif speedOffset-1 < Vs and speedOffset+1 > Vs then clr(f,0,0) lne(27,i,24,i) end
--calculate position of speed bug if speed-((32-15)*(speedTapeScale)) > speedSelect then speedBugPos=32 elseif speed-((0-15)*(speedTapeScale)) < speedSelect then speedBugPos=0 elseif (speedOffset-speedSelect) < (speedTapeScale) and (speedOffset-speedSelect) > -(speedTapeScale) then speedBugPos=i end
--set color of speed band if speedBandColors then if speedOffset > Vne then clr(f,0,0) elseif speedOffset > Va then clr(f,195,11) elseif speedOffset > Vs then clr(0,f,0) else clr(f,f,f) end else clr(f,f,f) end rctF(28,i,1,1)
end
--acceleration tape clr(f,0,f) lne(29,16,29,15-((accelPrint/maxAccel)*17))
--speed lable textbox if txtBoxEnable then clr(0,0,0) rctF(24-(string.len(round(speed,0,""))*5),12,(string.len(round(speed,0,""))*5)+1,7) clr(80,80,80) rct(23-(string.len(round(speed,0,""))*5),11,(string.len(round(speed,0,""))*5)+2,8) else clr(0,0,0,250) rctF(0,12,28,7) end
--blink speed if over Vne if speed > Vne and blnk then clr(f,0,0) else clr(220, 220, 220) end --text label txt(25-(string.len(round(speed,0,""))*5),13,round(speed,0,""))
